*Lawrence Michael Harvey Parsons, 6th Earl of Rosse (1906–1979)
*William Clere Leonard Brendan Parsons, 7th Earl of Rosse (born 1936)

The heir apparent is the present holder&#x27;s son, Lawrence Patrick Parsons, Lord Oxmantown (born 1969).
The heir apparent&#x27;s heir apparent is his son, the Hon. William Charles Yufan Parsons (born 2008).

